reviewText: Pretty good, I guess I remembered all three being funnier.
Three fun movies all on one disc! Excellent quality of both video and audio.
Arrived before scheduled delivery and good quality
I love it!  I don't  know how many times I watched these movies!  Always make me laugh!!  I recommend it!!
I purchased these movies as a new purchase. They arrived wrapped up in plastic but on the disks, they had some scratches and smudge marks on it.
